SuperSport has announced a new Showcase channel that will run from 17 December 2018 to 4 January 2019. The channel will remind viewers of the year’s biggest highlights, from the 2018 FIFA World Cup, to the Springboks’ win in Wellington. The channel will also screen various sport documentaries, including “Fire in Babylon” and “Strokes of Genius.” A series of football documentaries called “The Immortals” will also highlight the careers of some of the best footballers. The channel will feature all the tennis and golf majors, as well as the Commonwealth Games and Winter Olympics. Rugby fanatics can watch a variety of historical Rugby World Cup footage, as well as content focused on the Japan 2019 World Cup. The channel will be available on DStv packages ranging from Premium to Access.